  <brief_title>The EVICEL® Neurosurgery Phase III Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-Blinded, Randomized, Controlled Study to Evaluate the Safety and Effectiveness of EVICEL® Fibrin Sealant (Human) Compared to a Hydrogel Sealant as an Adjunct to Sutured Dural Repair</official_title>
