  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of EVICEL® Fibrin Sealant
      (Human) for use as an adjunct to sutured dural repair in cranial surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
